The '''null-burst projector''' was a ship-based weapon used by the [[Aing-Tii/Legends|Aing-Tii]] on their [[Sanhedrim ship]]s.

==Description==
The projector created a pocket of negative energy which did little physical damage to its target. However, the target's victims were incapacitated for several hours after the blast, during which time the user could board the ship without resistance.

